ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project demonstrates how to perform data aggregation and exploratory analysis 
using Python and Pandas. The notebook focuses on grouping, summarizing, 
and analyzing structured data to extract meaningful insights from a dataset.

The project uses common aggregation techniques such as groupby, mean, sum, count, 
and descriptive statistics, making it suitable for beginners and intermediate learners in data analysis.

